The paper discusses cooperative database systems, which are commonly studied in the field of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses operators for query relaxation, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed heuristics for assigning a degree of similarity to tuples in an answer table are related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and deep learning (cs.DL).
